\c 36
\s Jehoahazi naJehoyakimu naJehoyakini madzimambo aJudha
\p
\v 1 Zvino vanhu venyika iyo vakatora Jehoahazi mwanakomana waJosiya, ndokumugadza kuva mambo pachinzvimbo chababa vake paJerusarema.
\v 2 Jehoahazi waiva nemakore makumi maviri nematatu paakava mambo, ndokutonga mwedzi mitatu paJerusarema.
\v 3 Mambo weEgipita ndokumubvisa paJerusarema, ndokuripisa nyika matarenda zana esirivha netarenda regoridhe.
\v 4 Mambo weEgipita ndokugadza Eriyakimi munin'ina wake kuva mambo pamusoro paJudha neJerusarema, ndokushandura zita rake kuva Jehoyakimu. Neko ndokutora munin'ina wake Joahazi, ndomuisa kuEgipita.
\p
\v 5 Jehoyakimu waiva nemakore makumi maviri nemashanu paakava mambo; ndokutonga makore gumi nerimwe paJerusarema; ndokuita zvakaipa pameso paJehovha Mwari wake.
\v 6 Kwakakwira kumurwisa Nebhukadhinezari mambo weBhabhironi, ndokumusunga nemaketani ematare kumuisa kuBhabhironi.
\v 7 Nebhukadhinezari wakauisa \add imwe\add* yemidziyo yeimba yaJehovha kuBhabhironi ndokuiisa mutembere yake kuBhabhironi.
\p
\v 8 Zvino dzimwe dzenyaya dzaJehoyakimu, nezvinyangadzo zvake zvaakaita, nezvakawanikwa maari, tarirai zvakanyorwa mubhuku remadzimambo aIsraeri naJudha. Jehoyakini mwanakomana wake ndokuva mambo pachinzvimbo chake.
\p
\v 9 Jehoyakini waiva nemakore masere paakava mambo, ndokutonga mwedzi mitatu nemazuva gumi paJerusarema; ndokuita zvakaipa pameso paJehovha.
\v 10 Zvino pakudzoka kwegore, mambo Nebhukadhinezari wakatuma \add nhume\add* ndokuuya naye kuBhabhironi, pamwe nemidziyo inoshuvika yeimba yaJehovha, ndokuita munin'ina wake Zedhekia mambo pamusoro paJudha neJerusarema.
\s Zedhekia mambo wekupedzisira waJudha
\p
\v 11 Zedhekia waiva nemakore makumi maviri nerimwe paakava mambo; ndokutonga makore gumi nerimwe paJerusarema.
\v 12 Zvino wakaita zvakaipa pameso paJehovha Mwari wake; haana kuzvininipisa pamberi paJeremiya muporofita, \add aitaura \add*kubva mumuromo waJehovha.
\s Nebhukadhinezari anoputsa Jerusarema nekutapa vaJudha
\p
\v 13 Uye wakamukirawo mambo Nebhukadhinezari waiva amupikisa naMwari; asi wakaomesa mutsipa wake, ndokusimbisa moyo wake zvekuti haana kutendeukira kuna Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri.
\p
\v 14 Uye vakuru vese vevapristi nevanhu vakadarika zvikuru sezvinyangadzo zvese zvevahedheni, ndokusvibisa imba yaJehovha yaaiva aita tsvene paJerusarema.
\v 15 Zvino Jehovha Mwari wemadzibaba avo wakatuma \add mashoko\add* kwavari neruoko rwenhume dzake, achimuka mangwanani achituma, nokuti waiva netsitsi nevanhu vake uye nenzvimbo yake yekugara.
\v 16 Asi vaiseka nhume dzaMwari, ndokuzvidza mashoko ake, ndokusveveredza vaporofita vake, kusvika hasha dzaJehovha dzamukira vanhu vake, kusvika pasisina kurapika.
\v 17 Naizvozvo wakakwidza pavari mambo weVaKaradhiya uyo wakauraya majaya avo nemunondo muimba yavo tsvene; uye haana kunzwira tsitsi jaya kana musikana, munhu mukuru kana mutana; wakapa vese muruoko rwake.
\v 18 Nemidziyo yose yeimba yaMwari, mikuru nemidiki, nefuma yeimba yaJehovha, nefuma yamambo neyemachinda ake, zvese wakauisa kuBhabhironi.
\v 19 Zvino vakapisa imba yaMwari, ndokuputsa rusvingo rweJerusarema, nemizinda yayo yose vakapisa nemoto, ndokuparadza midziyo yayo yose inoshuvika.
\v 20 Zvino avo vakasara pamunondo wakavatapira kuBhabhironi, kwavakava varanda kwaari nevanakomana vake, kusvika kwava pakutonga kweushe hwePeresia;
\v 21 kuzadzisa shoko raJehovha, mumuromo waJeremiya, kusvika nyika yafarira masabata ayo; mazuva ese ekuparadzwa vakachengeta sabata, kusvika pakuzara kwemakore makumi manomwe.
\s Koreshi mambo wePerisiya unotendera VaJudha kudzoka
\p
\v 22 Zvino mugore rekutanga raKoreshi mambo wePerisiya, kuti shoko raJehovha \add rarehwa\add* nemuromo waJeremiya ripedzisike, Jehovha akamutsa mweya waKoreshi mambo wePerisiya, wakapfuudza inzwi nepaushe hwake hwese, uyewo mukunyora, achiti:
\p
\v 23 Ndizvo zvinoreva Koreshi mambo wePerisiya: Jehovha Mwari wekumatenga wakandipa ushe hwese hwenyika, uye iye wakandiraira kumuvakira imba paJerusarema riri paJudha. Ndiani ari pakati penyu wevanhu vake vose? Jehovha Mwari wake ngaave naye, uye ngaakwire.